                We built our process to be simple, transparent, and low-stress—especially 
                if you've had a bad experience with IT providers in the past.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-5 align-items-start">
            <!-- Process Steps -->
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="row g-4">
                    <!-- Step 1 -->
