                                We start with a conversation—no scripts, no pressure. We learn 
                                how your business operates, what systems you rely on, and what 
                                keeps you up at night.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 2 -->
                    <div class="col-12 d-flex">
                        <div class="me-3">
                            <span class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle bg-warning text-dark fw-bold" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                                2
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-1 text-white">Assess &amp; Prioritize</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-light text-opacity-75">
                                We review your current security posture and IT setup, identify 
                                real-world risks, and prioritize them based on impact and 
                                likelihood—not just headlines.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 3 -->
                    <div class="col-12 d-flex">
                        <div class="me-3">
                            <span class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle bg-warning text-dark fw-bold" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                                3
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-1 text-white">Implement Practical Protections</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-light text-opacity-75">
                                We design and deploy solutions that fit your size, budget, 
                                and compliance needs—backups, access controls, monitoring, 
                                user training, and more.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Step 4 -->
                    <div class="col-12 d-flex">
                        <div class="me-3">
                            <span class="d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle bg-warning text-dark fw-bold" style="width: 40px; height: 40px;">
                                4
                            </span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-1 text-white">Monitor, Support &amp; Improve</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0 text-light text-opacity-75">
                                Cybersecurity isn't a one-time project. We continuously monitor, 
                                update, and fine-tune your protections while keeping you informed 
                                with human-friendly updates.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Mission & Vision -->
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded-4 h-100" style="background-color: #1a1a1a;">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <p class="text-uppercase small fw-semibold text-warning mb-2">
                            Mission &amp; Vision
                        </p>
                        <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-3 text-white">Why We Do What We Do</h3>

                        <h4 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1 text-white">Our Mission</h4>
                        <p class="mb-3 text-light text-opacity-75">
                            To provide Orange County small and mid-sized businesses with 
                            enterprise-grade cybersecurity and IT support delivered with 
                            clarity, honesty, and a human touch.
                        </p>

                        <h4 class="h6 fw-bold mb-1 text-white">Our Vision</h4>
                        <p class="mb-0 text-light text-opacity-75">
                            A local business community where owners no longer fear technology 
                            or cyber threats, but instead use them confidently to grow and innovate.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

